[12:17:15    29]  - [done] Removed the non-exported raw parser façades (`cJSON_ParseWithOpts`, `cJSON_ParseWithLengthOpts`, `cJSON_Parse`, and `cJSON_ParseWithLength`). Their ABI work now lives only in the matching exported `*_ffi` entry points.
